MAHONEY v. WARDEN OF MARYLAND PENITENTIARY [App. No. 112,

September Term, 1964.]

Decided March 11, 1965.

Before Prescott, C. J., and Hammond, Hornby, Marbury and OppBnheimer, JJ.

Per Curiam:.

Application for leave to appeal from a denial of post conviction relief is denied for the reasons set out in the opinion of Judge Barnes in the court below.

Application denied.
